Controllers for MVC.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    App is a controller of sorts that contains a series of methods for logging in and miscellaneous tasks.
    ClaimListController
    Controller for ClaimsList.
    LoginController
    Logs a user in by checking Elastic search and stores their username in shared_preferences for offline logins.
    SettingsController
    Bridges Java objects and SharedPreferences, saves and loads items.
    TagsManager
    Controls the tags that are shown in TagManagerActivity.
